    "Research can focus on effective ways to educate AI practitioners and organisations about the risks and mitigation strategies related to offensive AI and adversarial AI attacks.Having discussed the implications of offensive AI and adversarial AI, let's explore how these findings inform the development of mitigation strategies for AI-driven cyberattacks.",
